QuestData.Title: Dumphry's Request
QuestData.Description: Fel orcs might be complete barbarians but their smithing is not as primitive as you might think. Only fel iron can be used with this mold if we want to end up with a working key - anything else would probably end up breaking it.$B$BBring me some fel iron bars, a bit of arcane dust and motes of fire. I'll try my hand at it, but I make no promises.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring 4 Fel Iron Bars, 2 Arcane Dust and 4 Motes of Fire to Dumphry at Honor Hold in Hellfire Peninsula.
QuestData.CompletionText: Have you obtained the materials I requested?
QuestData.RewardText: Let's try it then. Let's see what fel orc crafting is all about.
